  <p>
    This is a standard identity used in textbooks and calculators. It is <strong>not</strong> a substitute for a bank’s
    exact day-count method, leap-year handling, or promotional terms. When you enter APY in Nestfigure, the tool
    converts APY to an equivalent nominal rate for the selected compounding mode so a one-year horizon aligns with the
    stated APY under that model—see
